ass="xl6629924" style="height: 18pt;"></td><td class="xl7129924">　</td><td class="xl7629924">기말 이연법인세자산:</td><td class="xl7729924"></td><td class="xl7729924"></td><td class="xl7529924">　</td><td class="xl6629924"></td></tr><tr height="24" style="height: 18pt;"><td height="24" class="xl6629924" style="height: 18pt;"></td><td class="xl7129924">　</td><td class="xl7629924"><span lang="EN-US">(45,000 × 8 × 2/3 × 0.40) =</span></td><td class="xl8129924"><span lang="EN-US">96,000 </span></td><td class="xl8129924"></td><td class="xl7529924">　</td><td class="xl6629924"></td></tr><tr height="24" style="height: 18pt;"><td height="24" class="xl6629924" style="height: 18pt;"></td><td class="xl7129924">　</td><td class="xl7629924">기초 이연법인세자산의 차감</td><td class="xl8229924"><span lang="EN-US">(33,333)</span></td><td class="xl8129924"></td><td class="xl7529924">　</td><td class="xl6629924"></td></tr><tr height="24" style="height: 18pt;"><td height="24" class="xl6629924" style="height: 18pt;"></td><td class="xl7129924">　</td><td class="xl7629924">당기의 이연법인세수익</td><td class="xl8129924"></td><td class="xl8229924"><span lang="EN-US">62,667*</span></td><td class="xl7529924">　</td><td class="xl6629924"></td></tr><tr height="6" style="height: 4.95pt;"><td height="6" class="xl6629924" style="height: 4.95pt;"></td><td class="xl7829924">　</td><td class="xl7929924">　</td><td class="xl7929924">　</td><td class="xl7929924">　</td><td class="xl8029924">　</td><td class="xl6629924"></td></tr><tr height="6" style="height: 4.95pt;"><td height="6" class="xl6629924" style="height: 4.95pt;"></td><td class="xl6629924"></td><td class="xl6629924"></td><td class="xl6629924"></td><td class="xl6629924"></td><td class="xl6629924"></td><td class="xl6629924"></td></tr><tr height="23" style="height: 17.4pt;"><td height="23" class="xl6629924" style="height: 17.4pt;"></td><td colspan="2" class="xl6629924">*이 금액은 다음 방식으로 구성한다.</td><td class="xl6629924"></td><td class="xl6629924"></td><td class="xl6629924"></td><td class="